expression = re.compile(rfc._MAX_AGE_AV_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['Max-age=1234', 'Max-Age=0', 'Max-Age=a', 'Max=1', 'Max-Age=']
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad Max-Age AV '{m}' matched by regex".format(m=bad_example))
